latestPosts.caption:
I was at this restaurant @urbanroastdc in Washington DC when a guy proposed to his girlfriend and one of them had a cute baby girl who looked at me and smiled during the proposal, it was just so thoughtful to have that little girl there, and the proposal was so beautiful it literally made me cry. I went to the restaurant for its beautiful cherry blossom aesthetics (they change their aesthetics every season, that’s so cool) but I witnessed a live proposal and it just made my day. 
@urbanroastdc for hopeless romantics like me!
